  "detailed_description": "<h1>Room In Dream---Version 2.0 Playtest Now Open!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/95a07bfb56245f1edf053d2fcf2ec84b.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1024 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dear players,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your experience has always been the heart of our work.<br>Since the beginning of <i>Room In Dream</i>, we’ve carried the love, trust, and expectations of so many players — a responsibility we hold dear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After much reflection and discussion, we decided in 2024 to pause updates for the original version and completely rebuild the game from the ground up.<br>After more than a year of rethinking and remaking, we’re proud to present the <strong>brand-new Version 2.0</strong> of <i>Room In Dream</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💫 <strong>The Playtest for Version 2.0 is now opening!</strong><br>You can download the Playtest build directly from the <i>Room In Dream</i> Steam store page and experience the new version.<br>If you encounter any bugs or issues, please feel free to contact us via any of our social media channels or by email —<br>your feedback means the world to us. 💌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠️ <strong>Save Data & Update Notice</strong><br>Because nearly all game assets, data structures, and backend systems have been rebuilt:<br>👉 Version 2.0 will <strong>not be compatible</strong> with previous 1.0 save data.<br>We sincerely hope for your understanding and support.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the playtest ends, <i>Room In Dream</i> will receive a <strong>free update</strong> to Version 2.0.<br>All future updates and new content will continue to build upon this new foundation.<br>We truly hope Version 2.0 will bring you a smoother, more beautiful, and more relaxing experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you, from the bottom of our hearts, for your support and patience.<br>Your warmth and encouragement keep us moving forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >— <i>Cat Head Games</i> 💛</p></p><br><h1>RoadMap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/b5592af2c4f1cc0d6882b8426aba56da.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=1350 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to a world -- Room In Dream -- that moves at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here, you can decorate your cottage, plant flowers and trees, and build your dream island — a peaceful place where time flows gently and every frame feels like a hand-painted illustration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/d6b7566177665e48a18f8bdb6e9f382a.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Creative Home Design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start from scratch — collect furniture, decorate your garden, and design your perfect layout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No limits, no pressure. Every click brings a touch of warmth and charm to your cozy little world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/3312f16900a14b5275b222a2cfe2d453.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/4f9952fe4daecc0ea19d2f58fc7a1f1c.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/02ad6e45f103bd7dd07bb9767d53b8f4.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/9c4e15b2a601963e94bc097d5550d6f0.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌱 <strong>Freedom to Build Your Island</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Edit terrain freely, shape your island’s landscape, and let nature become part of your home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a living ecosystem where adorable animals can settle and thrive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your island grow day by day — it feels like crafting your very own hidden paradise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/2140d27197a8c4fac958be137e359e6e.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/079bb772ecf0a01752a7fe9dddc4930a.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/90e5df0dc81ae9d90ca79b144bcd2313.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/6add769fc6f3705616d115a6c788622b.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍂 <strong>Feel The Flow of Time and Seasons</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A real-time clock keeps your world in sync with reality — sunlight, rain, and snow all dance through your Room In Dream.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want a gentle drizzle today? Just one click away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the passage of time, watch your plants grow under your care, and enjoy the breathtaking scenery of every season.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with nature — your lovingly tended plants might surprise you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your imagination to build your own ecosystem — who knows, maybe some curious animals will come to visit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/fe7dbeeb6969548e95f9695dd61b7856.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/44fc8c798f118ab293a5b37a733a3a68.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/ef03a89fa2302130a9c77946d1ad60cb.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/58d9ea92f2473e78dbfe9a077b447978.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/f820e0cfacdd3982f5ed7f9c21da0789.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎧 <strong>Focus & Companion Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Room In Dream isn’t just a game — it’s your cozy focus companion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Activate Pomodoro Timer and White Noise Mode to turn your cottage into a live desktop wallpaper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let it accompany you through study, work, or those quiet moments when you just need to pause and breathe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/09e244917819a9c372ea2b7ae88a11d8.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/c0b2382fd0c739e6e226daad3376ad9f.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/c58564399851838167665d8edd6d9ea8.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>Neighborly Connections</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different environments host animal neighbors with distinct personalities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now and then, you’ll receive heartfelt letters from them —</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >invitations to help decorate their homes, each with their own unique taste:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >some love the scent of the forest, others the glow of starlight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your designs will make their world a little more beautiful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/4478fda9247d72c6ae8464ece64e9f79.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=517 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <i>Room In Dream </i>is a game born for slow living:<br>no quests, no stress, only freedom, warmth, and the joy of creation.<br>May you find your rhythm, and a quiet kind of happiness, here.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to a world -- Room In Dream -- that moves at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here, you can decorate your cottage, plant flowers and trees, and build your dream island — a peaceful place where time flows gently and every frame feels like a hand-painted illustration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/d6b7566177665e48a18f8bdb6e9f382a.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Creative Home Design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start from scratch — collect furniture, decorate your garden, and design your perfect layout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No limits, no pressure. Every click brings a touch of warmth and charm to your cozy little world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/3312f16900a14b5275b222a2cfe2d453.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/4f9952fe4daecc0ea19d2f58fc7a1f1c.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/02ad6e45f103bd7dd07bb9767d53b8f4.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/9c4e15b2a601963e94bc097d5550d6f0.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragra