h nature — your lovingly tended plants might surprise you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your imagination to build your own ecosystem — who knows, maybe some curious animals will come to visit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/fe7dbeeb6969548e95f9695dd61b7856.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/44fc8c798f118ab293a5b37a733a3a68.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/ef03a89fa2302130a9c77946d1ad60cb.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/58d9ea92f2473e78dbfe9a077b447978.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443960/extras/f820e0cfacdd3982f5ed7f9c21da0789.avif?t=1773854855\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎧 <strong>Focus & Companion Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Room In Dream isn’t just a game — it’s your cozy focus companion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Activate Pomodoro Timer and White Noise Mode to turn your cottage into a live desktop wallpaper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let it accompany you through study, work, or those quiet moments when you just need to pause and breathe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst